text: Novosukkulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 18 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Tuymazy, 7 km from Nikolayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Novosukkulovo
